TY  - JOUR
T1  - The Institute in Action—TIMS 1957 Presidential Address
AU  - Crane, Roger R.
Y1  - 1958/04/01
PY  - 1958
DA  - 1958/04/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.4.3.326
DO  - 10.1287/mnsc.4.3.326
T2  - Management Science
JF  - Management Science
JO  - Management Science
SP  - 326
EP  - 331
VL  - 4
IS  - 3
PB  - INFORMS
N2  - My predecessors, the three former presidents of The Institute of Management Sciences, have already established something of a tradition for the TIMS presidential address. Having been involved with the affairs of the Institute during most of a year, they talked about its aims and activities. This address also will concern these activities; in fact, that is its title: The Institute in Action. Before this address is over I hope you will have reflected on something which you already know and that you will carry this thought with you, if no other, when you leave. You are the Institute and the Institute in Action is you in action.
