N2  - The Editors of Management Science believes that it would be of value to its readers to establish a section entitled RECENT ARTICLES OF INTEREST, which will consist of reviews or abstracts of relevant articles. In addition to the many journals published in the English language, we would like to provide coverage of journals printed in French, German, Spanish, Italian, Japanese, etc. Accordingly, we would welcome hearing from any individual interested in, and willing to read such foreign language journals, and who would submit a brief review or abstract of all articles that would be of interest to Management Science readers. Subscriptions to the respective journals would be provided for these reviewers.
